  • Class Summary

    Cineplex class contains information such as cinemas, cineplex name.
    Movie
    Movie contains details on each movie.
    MovieShowing
    MovieShowing class contains information such as showtime, cinema and cineplex.
    MovieTicket
    MovieTicket is used during booking.
    Payment
    Payment class contains information when customer books a ticket
    Review
    Review object contains user's review and rating for a Movie.
    Seat
    Seat Class contains details for each seat in a cinema
    User
    User Class is used for accessing customer/staff functionality and to determine if user exits application.
